\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2690112 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3949159\charrsid1710208 And he'd come to London later on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9966907 H  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3949159\charrsid1710208 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2690112 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3949159\charrsid1710208 Do you think he actually enjoyed his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9966907 H  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3949159\charrsid1710208 
Oh yes, he was very interested in his work. And - he could have - taken on - several jobs when we went to Surrey but - people, used to come on a Sunday and want them done, and - but I mean it was weekends when he wanted to - improve things in our h
ouse. That - he found - you know, and he said it's only the weekends I'm home with the family most of the time and - they did - they - didn't expect to pay him, they just thought he'd - do things and - all for nothing, well - that wasn't - all that good e
n
ough to give up your weekend - I mean they try to do them themselves, think the knew, but as he said - you've got to be in the trade to know it, you can't just - fiddle with things you don't know anything about. Then he'd have - more of a job to put it ri
ght.
\par 
