{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}St John's Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, still in Highgate. Not too fr - from - the first home. And - we had - two rooms there. And - quite happy. And - then I - after we'd been there quite a while, of course my husband had had country jobs in between, where I used to go and stay. And - o
h - I had - see, that was {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}St John's Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, I think that's where I had my first baby. Next door to my mother there was a ground - floor flat going, with three rooms. And - we went - to live there then, having the baby and - so -
